item.title: CVE-2018-7498|2024-09-16T22:55:54.087Z -- philips -- philips%20alice%206%20system
item.description: In Philips Alice 6 System version R8.0.2 or prior, the lack of proper data encryption passes up the guarantees of confidentiality, integrity, and accountability that properly implemented encryption conveys.
